net.viktorc.detroid.framework.gui.dialogs

Class TimeSettingsDialog

  • Object
    • Dialog<TimeControl>
      • TimeSettingsDialog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventTarget

    public class TimeSettingsDialog
extends Dialog<TimeControl>
    A dialog that allows the time controls of a chess game to be set by displaying modifiable text input fields representing the time controls. When saved, the time control represented by the contents of the text input fields is returned by the showAndWait method.
    Author:
    Viktor
